title: Wall Street Breakfast July 15: 'Oil for Security' Back in Play as Biden Heads to Saudi Arabia
author: Seeking Alpha

description: 'Oil for security' back in play as Biden heads to Saudi Arabia. Amazon plans further 4,000 UK jobs despite global slowdown, Amazon trims its private-label selection due to weak sales, considers exiting business under regulatory pressure. Catch today’s WSB article here.
